- M2 `mergeSynonyms` LLM / [`promptOntologyRefine.ts`](extension/src/llm/promptOntologyRefine.ts) in production merge
- P7 `llmMergeRefine` / [`mergeWithLlm`](extension/src/store/mergeLlm.ts)
